me time to process.

00:11:10.962 --> 00:11:12.547 position:50% align:center
[ENDEAVOR]
Hmph.

00:11:12.630 --> 00:11:16.176 position:50% align:center
So. Y'wanted to talk?

00:11:19.763 --> 00:11:21.181 position:50% align:center
