than anyone else.

00:11:39.115 --> 00:11:42.786 position:50% align:center
Besting my own personal records.

00:11:42.869 --> 00:11:45.955 position:50% align:center
And yet... I can feel it.

00:11:46.039 --> 00:11:48.458 position:50% align:center
Some unseen thing
that you built up

00:11:48.541 --> 00:11:53.463 position:50% align:center
