is beginning to crumble.

00:11:53.546 --> 00:11:56.341 position:50% align:center
What does it mean
to be a symbol?

00:11:56.424 --> 00:12:00.720 position:50% align:center
That's what I want
to know. All Might.

00:12:09.646 --> 00:12:11.231 position:50% align:center
Give those back!

00:12:11.314 --> 00:12:13.358 position:50% align:center
They aren't toys, ya damn brats!

00:12:13.441 --> 00:12:16.319 position:50% align:center
Did they really swipe your
gauntlets that easily? How?

00:12:16.403 --> 00:12:18.405 position:50% align:center
I took them off because
it's too dangerous

00:12:18.488 --> 00:12:19.656 position:50% align:center
