00:12:19.739 --> 00:12:21.408 position:50% align:center
[growls]

00:12:21.491 --> 00:12:22.659 position:50% align:center
I mean, "winning
your hearts" is, like,

00:12:22.742 --> 00:12:23.910 position:50% align:center
super vague, you know?

00:12:23.993 --> 00:12:25.537 position:50% align:center
What are we even supposed
to be doing here?

00:12:25.620 --> 00:12:26.871 position:50% align:center
