00:12:26.955 --> 00:12:28.456 position:50% align:center
[hisses]

00:12:28.540 --> 00:12:30.542 position:50% align:center
[PRESENT MIC] Team Fish Turds
looks like they've completely

00:12:30.625 --> 00:12:33.336 position:50% align:center
lost the beat and are
flailing like flounder!

00:12:33.420 --> 00:12:36.589 position:50% align:center
Try not to go overboard.
This is still a training course.

00:12:36.673 --> 00:12:38.091 position:50% align:center
Roger that, yo!

00:12:38.174 --> 00:12:40.719 position:50% align:center
Let's hear from their teacher.
Got any special requests?

00:12:40.802 --> 00:12:42.721 position:50% align:center
What do those kiddos need?

00:12:42.804 --> 00:12:44.431 position:50% align:center
So much.

00:12:46.182 --> 00:12:48.268 position:50% align:center
