00:13:07.704 --> 00:13:10.874 position:50% align:center
I understand that this
is my responsibility.

00:13:10.957 --> 00:13:12.083 position:50% align:center
But, still,

00:13:12.167 --> 00:13:13.918 position:50% align:center
I hope meeting heroes
who're working hard

00:13:14.002 --> 00:13:16.629 position:50% align:center
to achieve their dreams
will help lead these kids

00:13:16.713 --> 00:13:18.965 position:50% align:center
down a more respectable path.

00:13:23.011 --> 00:13:25.680 position:50% align:center
There's no time for us
to bicker with each other.

00:13:25.764 --> 00:13:26.890 position:50% align:center
We have to save them.

00:13:26.973 --> 00:13:28.183 position:50% align:center
In other words,

00:13:28.266 --> 00:13:31.311 position:50% align:center
all we have to do is
make friends. No problem!

00:13:31.394 --> 00:13:34.439 position:50% align:center
[KATSUKI] Let's get this
babysitting over and done with.

00:13:34.522 --> 00:13:36.816 position:50% align:center
I'm ready to go back
to some actual training!

00:13:36.900 --> 00:13:39.361 position:50% align:center
[PRESENT MIC] Maybe try not
to make that angry face, Bakugo!

00:13:39.444 --> 00:13:41.112 position:50% align:center
[GANG ORCA yells]

