[PRESENT MIC] Now, how will UA's
walking explosion handle this?

00:13:45.533 --> 00:13:47.410 position:50% align:center
The stupid teacher
didn't fulfill her role

00:13:47.494 --> 00:13:50.413 position:50% align:center
