are following.

00:14:00.674 --> 00:14:03.343 position:50% align:center
We just gotta figure
out who it is.

00:14:03.426 --> 00:14:04.594 position:50% align:center
And then?

00:14:04.678 --> 00:14:06.388 position:50% align:center
[KATSUKI] We beat 'em up
and hang 'em from a post

00:14:06.471 --> 00:14:08.014 position:50% align:center
