was for us to be nice.

00:14:17.315 --> 00:14:20.985 position:50% align:center
Wow. Bakugo certainly
has a unique perspective.

00:14:22.320 --> 00:14:24.948 position:50% align:center
Whichever one of you is
the strongest, step up!

00:14:25.031 --> 00:14:26.533 position:50% align:center
Come fight me!

00:14:26.616 --> 00:14:28.243 position:50% align:center
[PRESENT MIC]
Dial it back, son!

00:14:28.326 --> 00:14:31.913 position:50% align:center
