way of solving problems.

00:14:31.996 --> 00:14:33.623 position:50% align:center
[KATSUKI growls]

00:14:33.707 --> 00:14:35.667 position:50% align:center
You're showing
your true colors.

00:14:35.750 --> 00:14:37.585 position:50% align:center
[PRESENT MIC]
Burned by an ankle biter!

00:14:37.669 --> 00:14:39.963 position:50% align:center
Enough already! Just bring it!

00:14:40.046 --> 00:14:42.549 position:50% align:center
Um, sir. Please forgive
me if this comes across

00:14:42.632 --> 00:14:46.094 position:50% align:center
as ungrateful, but are
the kids gonna be okay?

00:14:46.177 --> 00:14:48.638 position:50% align:center
Just sit back and
watch the show.

00:14:48.722 --> 00:14:50.515 position:50% align:center
Delinquents aren't
in fashion, you know.

00:14:50.598 --> 00:14:51.766 position:50% align:center
