to becoming friends.

00:14:55.687 --> 00:14:57.480 position:50% align:center
Who wants to be a hero?

00:14:57.564 --> 00:14:59.190 position:50% align:center
[PRESENT MIC]
Shiketsu takes the stage!

00:14:59.274 --> 00:15:00.567 position:50% align:center
--[BOY 79G] I do!
