I might have a better way.

00:16:15.308 --> 00:16:18.853 position:50% align:center
Oh? Why don't you show us
what you have in mind.

00:16:18.937 --> 00:16:21.439 position:50% align:center
I'm sure this is gonna be good.

00:16:21.523 --> 00:16:22.982 position:50% align:center
[TODOROKI]
Right.

00:16:24.442 --> 00:16:25.735 position:50% align:center
