by the time I was 20.

00:16:38.123 --> 00:16:41.126 position:50% align:center
And because I'd
carved my own path,

00:16:41.209 --> 00:16:45.005 position:50% align:center
I understood.

00:16:45.088 --> 00:16:48.925 position:50% align:center
There was no way I was ever
going to reach the top.

00:16:52.429 --> 00:16:55.265 position:50% align:center
