00:18:37.325 --> 00:18:40.203 position:50% align:center
But you and I are
not the same person.

00:18:40.286 --> 00:18:42.288 position:50% align:center
It was my decision
to become a symbol.

00:18:42.372 --> 00:18:45.667 position:50% align:center
But you don't have
to do that. Instead,

00:18:45.750 --> 00:18:51.256 position:50% align:center
