[inhales]

00:19:40.305 --> 00:19:42.057 position:50% align:center
My name is not "Five Wienies."

00:19:42.140 --> 00:19:45.185 position:50% align:center
I am Shoto from UA,
and I wanna be a hero.

00:19:45.268 --> 00:19:47.937 position:50% align:center
My father, Endeavor, is
currently the number-one hero,

00:19:48.021 --> 00:19:49.814 position:50% align:center
